name: P E R S O N A

metadata.name: .fear
metadata.description:
.fear tells a story about how we as a human overcome our fear with gathering all the courage we have.

You can't face fear without knowing about yourself first.

-----

PERSONA is a collection about inner demons and how they're trying to conquer us in any way possible. Stop avoiding them. Stop fighting them. Instead, learn to make peace with your demons.
